description: The folks of Klamath Falls have absolutely fallen for the deliciously fresh and Southern fried selection that they’re serving over at the Chick ‘N’ Dish truck. This talented and passionate team uses only fresh (never frozen) locally sourced chicken to create their incredibly tasty dishes. You simply must try their Boneless Chick ‘N’ Fritter Basket, or the BBQ Chick ‘N’ Quesadilla, or Smothered Chick ‘N’ Biscuit, fresh buttermilk biscuit topped with your choice of smotherings, including Fried Chicken & Country Sausage Gravy. Oh, and for dessert? How about the local favorite and ever-so-famous Banana Puddin’...If your mouth is watering (which, you know, it probably is), then you just gotta get yourself over to Chick ‘N’ Dish quick.
name: Chick 'N' Dish
